  "Start as CryptoKnight by directly referring someone using your invite code. Note: You only earn when your referrals trade": "通过使用你的邀请代码直接推荐某人来开始成为CryptoKnight。注意：只有当你的推荐人进行交易时，你才会获得奖励。",
