  "What is the NightTrader Exchange referral system?": "什么是NightTrader Exchange推荐系统？",
  "The NightTrader Exchange referral system is a 5-tier program that rewards users for bringing new traders to the platform. As you progress through the tiers, you earn a percentage of the trade fees generated by your referrals and their subsequent referrals.": "NightTrader Exchange推荐系统是一个5级计划，奖励用户为平台带来新的交易者。随着你在各个级别的进展，你将赚取由你的推荐人及其后续推荐人产生的交易费用的一定比例。",
  "How do I join the referral program?": "如何加入推荐计划？",
  "To join the referral program, simply sign up for a NightTrader Exchange account and start referring new users with your unique invite code.": "要加入推荐计划，只需注册NightTrader Exchange账户，并开始使用你的唯一邀请代码推荐新用户。",
  "How do I become a CryptoKnight?": "如何成为CryptoKnight？",
  "You become a CryptoKnight by directly referring someone to NightTrader Exchange using your invite code.": "通过使用你的邀请代码直接推荐某人到NightTrader Exchange，你就可以成为CryptoKnight。",
  "Do I earn rewards if my referrals don't trade?": "如果我的推荐人不进行交易，我能获得奖励吗？",
  "No, you only earn rewards when your referrals actively trade on the platform.": "不，只有当你的推荐人积极在平台上进行交易时，你才会获得奖励。",
  "How do I progress to higher tiers?": "如何晋升到更高的级别？",
  "To progress to higher tiers, your referrals must also refer new users. For example, to become a CryptoBaron, your direct referrals must have their own referrals.": "要晋升到更高的级别，你的推荐人也必须推荐新用户。例如，要成为CryptoBaron，你的直接推荐人必须有自己的推荐人。",
  "Can I earn from multiple tiers simultaneously?": "我可以同时从多个级别获得收益吗？",
  "Yes, you can earn from multiple tiers simultaneously as long as you have referrals at different levels.": "是的，只要你有不同级别的推荐人，你就可以同时从多个级别获得收益。",
  "How are the earnings calculated for higher tiers?": "更高级别的收益如何计算？",
  "Higher tiers earn a percentage of the remaining trade fees after lower tiers have been paid out. For example, CryptoBarons earn 24% of the fees remaining after CryptoKnights have been paid.": "更高的级别在较低级别支付完后，获得剩余交易费用的百分比。例如，CryptoBarons获得在CryptoKnights支付完后的24%的费用。",
  "Is there a limit to how many referrals I can have?": "我可以有多少推荐人？",
  "There is no limit to the number of referrals you can have at any tier.": "在任何级别，都没有推荐人数的限制。",
  "How can I maximize my earnings in the referral program?": "如何最大化我的推荐计划收益？",
  "To maximize your earnings: Invite active traders, encourage your referrals to refer others, aim to climb to higher tiers and stay engaged with your referral network.": "要最大化你的收益：邀请活跃的交易者，鼓励你的推荐人邀请其他人，争取晋升到更高的级别，并与推荐网络保持互动。",
  "How often are referral rewards paid out?": "推荐奖励多久发放一次？",
  "First every week after we do a maintaince usually on sunday. Later with more users it will be more frequently.": "首先，每周一次，通常是在我们周日进行维护后。随着用户增多，奖励将会更频繁发放。",
  "Can I track my referral earnings?": "我可以追踪我的推荐收益吗？",
  "Yes, you should be able to track your referral earnings through your NightTrader Exchange account dashboard. For detailed information, please check the platform or contact support.": "是的，你应该能够通过NightTrader Exchange账户仪表板追踪你的推荐收益。如需详细信息，请检查平台或联系支持。",
  "Faq": "常见问题",
  "Requirement: At least one direct referral": "要求：至少有一个直接推荐人",
  "Requirement: Your direct referrals must have their own referrals": "要求：你的直接推荐人必须有自己的推荐人",
  "Requirement: Your CryptoBaron referrals must have their own referrals": "要求：你的CryptoBaron推荐人必须有自己的推荐人",
  "Requirement: Your CryptoEarl referrals must have their own referrals": "要求：你的CryptoEarl推荐人必须有自己的推荐人",
  "Requirement: Your CryptoDuke referrals must have their own referrals": "要求：你的CryptoDuke推荐人必须有自己的推荐人",
  "Your earnings depend on your referrals' trading activity.": "你的收益取决于你推荐人的交易活动。",
